{% extends "base.jinja" %}
{% block title %}BoI Companion{% endblock %}
{% block scripts %}
    <script src="/static/js/utils.js" defer></script>
{% endblock %}
{% block contenu %}
    {% if error == true %}
        <div class="alert alert-dismissible alert-danger">
            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
            Steam ID is not valid. Change a few things up and try submitting again.
        </div>
    {% endif %}
    <section class="text-center p-5">
        <h1>Binding of Isaac Companion</h1>
        {% if not session and not session.steam_id %}
        <p>To have access to the companion, please enter your Steam/Profile ID bellow.</p>
        <form>
            <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                <input class="col-lg-3 col-10 p-2 m-1" type="text" id="steamid-input" name="steamid-input" placeholder="Steam Id...">
                <div class="col-lg-2 col-4 btn-stats-achievement" id="steamid-button">Let's go!</div>
                <div class="invalid-feedback" id="validation_steam_id"></div>
                <small class="form-text text-muted col-12"><a href="https://www.steamidfinder.com/">What is my steam id?</a>(Your steam profile needs to be set to public)</small>
            </div>
        </form>

        <h4 class="p-3">Or...</h4>
        <div class="steam_button text-center position-relative">
            <a href="/steamAuth" class="stretched-link">Log in with steam</a>
            <img src="/static/images/steam-logo-black-transparent.png" alt="SteamLogo" class="steam_logo">
        </div>
        {% endif %}
    </section>

    <section>
        <h4 class="mb-3 text-center">
            Some information about Isaac Companion
        </h4>
        <div class="row justify-content-around">
            <div class="card-info text-center col-xl-4 col-md-12 p-3">
                <h5>Purpose</h5>
                <img src="/static/images/Stage_Chest_room.webp" alt="MiroirStageImage" class="w-100 rounded">
                <p class="p-3">The goal of this website is to help you to begin your journey playing The Binding of Isaac. You will find plenty of tips and tricks to obtain the main achievements in the game so you can progress faster.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-info text-center col-xl-4 col-md-12 p-3">
                <h5>Achievements</h5>
                <img src="/static/images/Stage_Caves_room.webp" alt="CavesStageImage" class="w-100 rounded">
                <p class="p-3">Achievements in The Binding of Isaac are a huge part of the game. Each boss you kill will unlock a new item that will spawn in your next runs. In the tab "My Achievements", you can take a look at all the completion marks you have done with every character.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-info text-center col-xl-4 col-md-12 p-3">
                <h5>Help with runs</h5>
                <img src="/static/images/Stage_Corpse_room.webp" alt="CorpseStageImage" class="w-100 rounded">
                <p class="p-3">The companion can help doing your runs without forgeting any steps. Often, you forget about a little thing in your run and it ruins it, so with this website you won't forget anything anymore.</p>
            </div>
            <h5 class="text-center"><a href="/feedback">More informations...</a></h5>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}